A correctly formatted _index fille for a har containg a 1MB file foobar file should contain the following:
{noformat}
%2F dir 1508173657482+1023+hdfs+supergroup 0 0 foobar
%2Ffoobar file part-0 0 1048576 1508173512707+420+hdfs+supergroup
{noformat}

I just found out that in branch 3.0.0, the HarStatus except one index record except at least 5 parameters.

{code:java}
      this.name = decodeFileName(splits[0]);
      this.isDir = "dir".equals(splits[1]);
      // this is equal to "none" if its a directory
      this.partName = splits[2];
      this.startIndex = Long.parseLong(splits[3]);
      this.length = Long.parseLong(splits[4]);
{code}
I'll fix this issue by checking the number of parameters before we use them.
